<project name="LDAP Utilities">
	
	<!--    = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = =
	              macrodef: ldif.import
	        This Macrodef execute the LDAPImport command
	             = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = -->
	<macrodef name="ldif.import" >
		<attribute name="dir" default="${wt.home}"/>
		<attribute name="ldif.file" />
		<sequential>
			<exec-cmd executable="${wc_cmd}" failonerror="true" action="LDIF Import" parameters="[dir=@{dir}|ldif.file=@{ldif.file}]">
				<args>
					<arg line="${extra.java.args}" />
					<arg value="com.infoengine.util.LDAPImport" />
					<arg value="-dir" />
					<arg value="@{dir}" />
					<arg value="-ldiffile" />
					<arg value="@{ldif.file}" />
				</args>
			</exec-cmd>
		</sequential>
	</macrodef>
	
</project>
